# Tests Directory

This directory contains Playwright E2E test files.

## Tests to be created (Phase 3 & 4):

- `family-creation.spec.ts` - Family creation wizard tests (converted from Cypress)
- `accessibility.spec.ts` - WCAG 2.1 AA compliance tests
- `event-chains.spec.ts` - Event-driven workflow tests
- `cross-browser.spec.ts` - Cross-browser smoke tests

## Naming Convention

All test files should end with `.spec.ts`

## Test Structure

```typescript
import { test, expect } from '@playwright/test';

test.describe('Feature Name', () => {
  test.beforeEach(async ({ page }) => {
    // Setup
  });

  test('should do something', async ({ page }) => {
    await test.step('Step 1', async () => {
      // Action
    });

    await test.step('Step 2', async () => {
      // Verification
    });
  });
});
```
